Package hms.doctor

package hms.doctor
Contains Doctor utils for Appointment/Outcome/Medical Record Management.

    Description

    Manages appointments for doctors in the Hospital Management System (HMS).

    Doctor
    Represents Doctors in the Hospital Management System (HMS).
